{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshnotificationui"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshnotificationui"]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"PushwooshNotificationUI","symbolKind":"module","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshNotificationUI"}],"title":"PushwooshNotificationUI","roleHeading":"Framework","role":"collection"},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesViewController"],"title":"Stories UI"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/StoryPage"],"title":"Payload model"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesDelegate"],"title":"Analytics"},{"title":"Media pre-cache","identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesMediaPrefetcher"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"PushwooshNotificationUI provides ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesViewController","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" — a drop-in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNNotificationContentExtension"},{"type":"text","text":" view controller that renders an Instagram-style"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"stories experience: full-bleed images, top progress bars, auto-advance, tap-zone","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"navigation, per-frame title\/subtitle, and an optional deep-link button."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The module links only UIKit, UserNotifications, and UserNotificationsUI (plus","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"CryptoKit for a stable cache key), so it adds no Pushwoosh Core\/Framework weight","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to your memory-constrained extension process.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"text":"Usage","type":"heading","anchor":"Usage"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In your Notification Content Extension:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["import PushwooshNotificationUI","","class NotificationViewController: PushwooshStoriesViewController {}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then set these keys in the extension’s Info.plist:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"UNNotificationExtensionCategory","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" = "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PW_STORIES"},{"type":"text","text":" (must match "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"aps.category"},{"text":")","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"UNNotificationExtensionUserInteractionEnabled","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" = ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"UNNotificationExtensionDefaultContentHidden","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" = "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNNotificationExtensionInitialContentSizeRatio"},{"text":" = e.g. ","type":"text"},{"code":"1.5","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" (keep in sync with "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesViewController\/storyAspectRatio"},{"text":")","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSExtensionPrincipalClass"},{"text":" = ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"$(PRODUCT_MODULE_NAME).NotificationViewController"},{"text":" (code-only, no storyboard)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"level":2,"text":"Payload","anchor":"Payload","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The stories are described by a ","type":"text"},{"code":"pw_stories","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" block, alongside an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"aps.category"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"matching "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNNotificationExtensionCategory"},{"type":"text","text":". The parser accepts the block either at"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"payload root","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g. via the Pushwoosh API "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ios_root_params"},{"text":") or inside the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"custom-data container "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"u"},{"text":" \/ ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userdata"},{"text":" (the Pushwoosh API ","type":"text"},{"code":"data","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" field — delivered as","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a dictionary or a JSON-encoded string). The root form on the device looks like this:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["{","  \"aps\": { \"category\": \"PW_STORIES\" },","  \"pw_stories\": { \"pages\": [","    { \"image\": \"https:\/\/...\/1.jpg\", \"duration\": 5.0,","      \"link\": \"myapp:\/\/sale\", \"button_title\": \"Buy\",","      \"title\": \"Summer Sale\", \"subtitle\": \"Up to 70% off\" },","    { \"image\": \"https:\/\/...\/2.jpg\" }","  ]}","}"],"syntax":"json"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sent through the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"data"},{"type":"text","text":" API field instead (recommended, since it does not depend on"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"ios_root_params","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"), the same block arrives nested under "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"u"},{"text":" — while ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"aps.category"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(and ","type":"text"},{"code":"mutable-content","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" for the pre-cache path) still go through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ios_root_params.aps"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"as there is no dedicated request field for them. The relevant createMessage fields:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"json","code":["{","  \"ios_root_params\": { \"aps\": { \"category\": \"PW_STORIES\", \"mutable-content\": 1 } },","  \"data\": { \"pw_stories\": { \"pages\": [ { \"image\": \"https:\/\/...\/1.jpg\" } ] } }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The parser tries the root first, then "},{"code":"u","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" \/ "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userdata"},{"type":"text","text":", so both delivery styles work"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and old pushes keep rendering."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Every field except "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"image"},{"text":" is optional. ","type":"text"},{"code":"link","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" (like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"image"},{"type":"text","text":") must include a URL"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"scheme. A missing, empty, or malformed payload falls back to the default content"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"(the alert body) without crashing — override "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesViewController\/showDefaultContent(for:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Analytics","text":"Analytics"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Set ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesViewController\/storiesDelegate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" to observe lifecycle and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"engagement and forward it to your analytics (the module itself sends nothing):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class NotificationViewController: PushwooshStoriesViewController, PushwooshStoriesDelegate {","    override func viewDidLoad() {","        super.viewDidLoad()","        storiesDelegate = self","    }","    func storiesViewController(_ c: PushwooshStoriesViewController, didTapActionFor page: StoryPage, at index: Int) {","        \/\/ forward the per-page click to your backend","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Instant--offline-first-frame-App-Group-pre-cache","text":"Instant \/ offline first frame (App Group pre-cache)"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To make the first frame appear instantly (and offline), pre-download the media in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"a Notification ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Service","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" Extension into a shared App Group container that the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Content Extension reads from:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enable the "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"App Groups","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" capability (same id) on both the Service and Content"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"extensions, and override "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesViewController\/appGroupIdentifier","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"From the Service Extension’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"didReceive(_:withContentHandler:)"},{"text":", call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesMediaPrefetcher\/prefetch(userInfo:appGroupIdentifier:completion:)","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Send the push with ","type":"text"},{"code":"mutable-content: 1","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so the Service Extension runs.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Without this, the module still works — images download on display instead.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A ready-made full-screen “stories” UI for an expanded push notification."}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI/documentation/PushwooshNotificationUI/StoryPage":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/StoryPage","title":"StoryPage","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshnotificationui\/storypage","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"StoryPage"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"StoryPage"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI/documentation/PushwooshNotificationUI/PushwooshStoriesViewController/showDefaultContent(for:)":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"showDefaultContent(for:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"k